        <mj-text font-size="16px" font-weight="300" text-transform="uppercase" letter-spacing="3px" align="left" padding-top="18px" padding-bottom="18px"><a href="https://brightland.co/blogs/recipes" class="menu-link" target="_blank">Recipes</a></mj-text>
